'''''First Expedition''''' is a 1988 video game published by [[Interstel Corporation]].

==Gameplay==
''First Expedition'' is a game in which a nautical simulation involves a quest to find three sun spheres that were stolen from the island of Shandola.<ref name="CGW53"/>

==Reception==
Dennis Owens reviewed the game for ''[[Computer Gaming World]]'', and stated that "Not recommended for adventure gamers unless they are interested in intricate navigational techniques."<ref name="CGW53">{{cite magazine |last=Owens |first=Dennis |title=Longing for Shandola: Interstel's "First Expedition" |magazine=Computer Gaming World |date=November 1988 |volume=1 |issue=53 |pages=22, 61}}</ref>

